- '2023 data cargo' refers to data files collected in the year 2023; 
- 'eye on the sky' is a metaphor for a telescope or observatory; 
- 'ID badge' number refers to the unique identifier for a telescope (telescope_id).

- High and medium quality data refers to a subjective measure of the data's reliability and accuracy; 
- The Kepler Telescope is a space telescope launched by NASA to discover exoplanets; 
